<p><a name="Three_Mile_Island_reactor_accident" id="Three_Mile_Island_reactor_accident"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Three_Mile_Island_accident&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Three Mile Island reactor accident">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Three Mile Island reactor accident</span></h2>
<p><a name="Understanding_pressurized_water_reactors" id="Understanding_pressurized_water_reactors"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Three_Mile_Island_accident&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Understanding pressurized water reactors">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Understanding pressurized water reactors</span></h3>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Pressurized_water_reactor" title="Pressurized water reactor">Pressurized water reactor</a></div>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-content" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
