<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFWalker2004">Walker, J. Samuel (2004). <i><a href="/wiki/Three_Mile_Island:_A_Nuclear_Crisis_in_Historical_Perspective" title="Three Mile Island: A Nuclear Crisis in Historical Perspective">Three Mile Island: A Nuclear Crisis in Historical Perspective</a></i>. Berkeley: University of California Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0520239407" class="internal">ISBN 0-520-23940-7</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BThree+Mile+Island%3A+A+Nuclear+Crisis+in+Historical+Perspective%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Walker&amp;rft.aufirst=J.+Samuel&amp;rft.au=Walker%2C+J.+Samuel&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.place=Berkeley&amp;rft.pub=University+of+California+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-520-23940-7&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Three_Mile_Island_accident"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (<a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=0EDwbQF5k24C&amp;dq=%22three+mile+island%22+%2B+books&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=bn&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=U9PLSbDxG4WEtwfz3qTaCQ&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;resnum=7#PPP9,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=0EDwbQF5k24C&amp;dq=%22three+mile+island%22+%2B+books&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=bn&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=U9PLSbDxG4WEtwfz3qTaCQ&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;resnum=7#PPP9,M1" rel="nofollow">Google Books</a>)</li>
