d_Nuclear_Generating_Station" title="Waterford Nuclear Generating Station">Waterford</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Wolf_Creek_Nuclear_Generating_Station" title="Wolf Creek Nuclear Generating Station" class="mw-redirect">Wolf Creek</a></span></p>
